    `â€¢ Network HID: 234187180623265792\n` +
    `â€¢ Campaign Filter: /tricky/i (INCLUDE)\n\n` +
    
    'ðŸ”¥ MOLOCO:\n' +
    `â€¢ Target eROAS: ${molocoTarget}%\n` +
