    `â€¢ Network HID: 445856363109679104\n` +
    `â€¢ Campaign Filter: NO FILTER (all campaigns)\n\n` +
    
    'ðŸ“ˆ REGULAR:\n' +
    `â€¢ Target eROAS: ${regularTarget}%\n` +
    `â€¢ Growth Thresholds: Healthy(${regularThresholds.healthyGrowth.minSpendChange}%/${regularThresholds.healthyGrowth.minProfitChange}%), Scaling(${regularThresholds.scalingDown.maxSpendChange}%)\n` +
    `â€¢ Network HID: 234187180623265792\n` +
    `â€¢ Campaign Filter: !/tricky/i (EXCLUDE)\n\n` +
    
    'âš™ï¸ AUTOMATION:\n' +
    `â€¢ Auto Cache: ${cacheEnabled ? 'âœ… Enabled (2 AM daily)' : 'âŒ Disabled'}\n` +
    `â€¢ Auto Update: ${updateEnabled ? 'âœ… Enabled (Monday 5 AM)' : 'âŒ Disabled'}\n\n` +
    
    'ðŸ“ FEATURES:\n' +
    'â€¢ Week-level comments: âœ… Supported\n' +
    'â€¢ Campaign-level comments: âœ… Supported\n' +
    'â€¢ Comment preservation: âœ… Active\n' +
    'â€¢ Group management: âœ… Auto-collapse\n' +
